CMake build, and the in-engine data extractor). It does NOT cover the original
ACiD Tetris game, its data file (ATET.DAT), or any assets contained therein.

ACiD Tetris and all of its assets are (C) Copyright 1997 Jason Pimble & Scott
Emerle / Dungeon Dwellers Design, distributed as freeware under the terms in
the original ATET.DOC (reproduced in NOTICE). This port ships none of that
content; it decodes it at runtime from a copy of the game you provide yourself.
See NOTICE and README.md.

